## Import


WAF Regional Geo Match Set can be imported using the id, e.g.

```sh
 $ pulumi import aws:wafregional/geoMatchSet:GeoMatchSet geo_match_set a1b2c3d4-d5f6-7777-8888-9999aaaabbbbcccc
```
